sentences: His first solo album, The Jane, Room 217, was released on August 24th, 2018, to near-universal acclaim from critics.
Jessee formed indie band Hotel Lights in 2004, with whom he has recorded 4 studio albums and an extended play.

Darren can also be heard drumming on the song "Strangest Thing" from The War on Drugs' 2017 album A Deeper Understanding, Hiss Golden Messenger's Hallelujah Anyhow (2017), and Josh Rouse's album Under Cold Blue Stars, released in 2002.
